each of the following search warrants issued by this Court  
1.   Warrant lssued April 21,  l99S,  at 3:10 p.m.  and designated as 
Case Number M-95-95-H;  
2.   Warrant issued April 21,  1995,  at 3:55 p.m.  and des gnated as 
Case Number M-95-96-Hi  
3.   Warrant lssued April 21,  1995,  at S:S5 p.m.  and designated 
as Case Number M-95-100-H;  
4.   Warrant  issued May  5,  l99S,  at  5:20  p.m.  and designated as 
