THE ASSOCIATED PRESS; THE DAILY OKLAHOMAN; THE 
TULSA WORLD, KFOR-TV CHANNEL 4; KWTV CHANNEL 
9; KJRH CHANNEL 2 (TULSA); SOCIETY OF 
PROFESSIONAL JOURNALISTS OKLAHOMA CITY 
CHAPTER; AND SOCIETY OF PROFESSIONAL 
JOURNALISTS EASTERN OKLAHOMA CHAPTER  
 
