 A.   Yes.

 Q.   Was it going east or west?

 A.   I believe east.

 Q.   Witness number three -- you said you had several -- number 

 three. 

 A.   There was another witness that advised that before -- 

 approximately 20 minutes before the bomb went off, that this 

