<P>Title: "First Day, Tuesday, 11/20/1945, Part 6: Appendix A: Statement of Individual Responsibility for Crimes Set Out In Counts One, Two, Three and Four: Ley", in Trial of the Major War Criminals before the International Military Tribunal. Volume II. Proceedings: 11/14/1945-11/30/1945. [Official text in the English language.] Nuremberg: IMT, 1947. pp. 75-77.</P>

